OL,3,CFleeing driver jailed for ramming
OL,4,Cpolice motorcyclist
OL,6,FWatch Police dash cam footage of car
OL,7,Fcrashing into officer's motorbike.
OL,9,FA Southampton man has been jailed for
OL,10,Ffour years for ramming a police
OL,11,Fmotorcyclist with a car.
OL,13,FMarvin Geddes, 33, fled from police
OL,14,Fofficers when they attempted to stop
OL,15,Fthe Honda Civic he was driving.
OL,17,FIt was spotted on Wimpson Lane,
OL,18,FSouthampton, at around 9.20pm on 2
OL,19,FJuly 2024 with suspected cloned plates.
