OL,6,FA short pursuit followed where Police
OL,7,Fsay the Honda was driven in an
OL,8,Fextremely dangerous manner, including
OL,9,Fgoing the wrong way around a
OL,10,Froundabout, driving on the wrong side
OL,11,Fof the road, and driving through a red
OL,12,Flight.
OL,14,FPC Derek Hearn, a motorcyclist with
OL,15,Fthe Roads Policing team, was involved
OL,16,Fin the pursuit of the Honda and was
OL,17,Fhit by the vehicle on Lords Hill
OL,18,FCentre East.
