OL,3,CFleeing driver jailed for ramming
OL,4,Cpolice motorcyclist
OL,6,FShocking dash cam footage from PC
OL,7,FHearn's police motorcycle showed the
OL,8,FHonda driver crashing into the officer
OL,9,Fat speed.
OL,11,FThe court heard Geddes did not stay at
OL,12,Fthe scene and sped off towards Lords
OL,13,FHill Centre West, where he was then
OL,14,Finvolved in a collision with a Peugeot
OL,15,F108.
OL,17,FGeddes then abandoned his Honda and
OL,18,Ffled the scene on foot.
