OL,3,CFleeing driver jailed for ramming
OL,4,Cpolice motorcyclist
OL,6,FThe Honda was later confirmed to have
OL,7,Fbeen stolen from an address in Roberts
OL,8,FRoad, Southampton, on 26 March 2023.
OL,10,FPC Hearn said: "I feel lucky that I
OL,11,Fhaven't lost a limb or even my life
OL,12,Ffrom this incident."
OL,14,F"As a police officer I pride myself on
OL,15,Fdoing my job to the best of my ability
OL,16,Fto safeguard the public. I do not
OL,17,Faccept that my life should be put in
OL,18,Fdanger because of that."
