OL,4,Cpolice motorcyclist
OL,6,FSuperintendent Mark Lewis said: "This
OL,7,Fis a stark reminder of the dangers our
OL,8,Fofficers sometimes face while simply
OL,9,Fdoing their jobs."
OL,11,F"I was absolutely appalled when I saw
OL,12,Fthe footage of this incident. No
OL,13,Fpolice officer should ever have to
OL,14,Fdeal with such extreme violence
OL,15,Ftowards them."
OL,17,F"The fact PC Hearn and the driver of
OL,18,Fthe Peugeot were not seriously injured
OL,19,Fis extremely lucky, considering the
OL,20,Fsevere level of complete disregard
OL,21,FGeddes showed to them."
