OL,6,FGeddes appeared at Southampton Crown
OL,7,FCourt and was given a 48-month
OL,8,Fsentence after previously pleading
OL,9,Fguilty to attempting to cause actual
OL,10,Fbodily harm, dangerous driving and
OL,11,Fdriving without a licence and driving
OL,12,Fwithout insurance.
